[The HPAI H5N8 event in Saudi Arabia, which reportedly started 19 Dec 2017, continues its spread. The 1st 4 outbreaks, as duly reported to the OIE until 2 Jan 2017, took place in Riyadh (http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?fupser=&dothis=&reportid=25487).

Epidemiological statistics of the 6 new outbreaks in 3 separate locations (item 1) and of the additional one in Makkah (item 2) are expected to be included in the next follow-up report to the OIE. - Mod.AS

HealthMap/ProMED maps can be found at: Saudi Arabia: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5539356,131.]
